article_id:2064,category_name:News,title_name:Gala Dragalia Is Now Live!,image_path:,message:<div>Gala Dragalia started on <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1616824800"></span>!</div><div><br></div><div>What are Gala Dragalia and Gala Dragalia Remix?</div><div>・The initial appearance rate for 5★ adventurers and dragons is boosted to 6%, which is up from the standard 4%! If you get a 5★ summon or 5★ featured summon, the appearance rate will return to the initial 6%.</div><div><span style="color: rgb(226, 80, 65);">・The newly added 5★ adventurer Myriam (wind) will also appear in the next summon showcase.</span></div><div><span style="color: rgb(226, 80, 65);">・The Platinum Showcase that is now live does not include the new adventurers added in this showcase.</span></div><div><br></div><div>Newly added featured adventurers:</div><div>5★ Gala Notte (wind/dagger)</div><div>5★ Myriam (wind/wand)</div><div><br></div><div>Gala Dragalia appearance rates:</div><div>5★ total: 6.00%</div><div>5★ featured total: 1.00% (Adventurers: 1.00%)</div><div>5★ standard total: 5.00% (Adventurers: 2.00%, Dragons: 3.00%)</div><div>4★ standard total: 16.00% (Adventurers: 8.55%, Dragons: 7.45%)</div><div>3★ standard total: 78.00% (Adventurers: 47.00%, Dragons: 31.00%)</div><div><br></div><div>Gala Dragalia event duration:</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1616824800"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1617343199"></span></div><div><br></div><div>Get a closer look at the newly added featured adventurers below.</div><div><br></div><div>
